					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">There are ways to make smoother animations even with the 32-pixel tiles. For example, <em>Yoshi's Cookie</em> for NES moves things 8 pixels at a time, which is smoother than 16. With 8-pixel movement, you'll have to avoid attribute clash somehow; that can be done by leaving an 8-pixel gap between tiles when moving them.</div>

